In [ ]:
# Class Imbalance problem:
#       - > employee who stayed and those left are improprtionate (0 = 9137, 1 = 2862(left))
#       - > emp stayed are almost three times that of the left count
#       - > the model will be biased towards the stayed numbers
#this is class imbalance problem
# to deal with this we apply statistical tools is  SMOTE Analysis
